# E-Commerce Web Application

## Overview

A full-stack E-Commerce web application built using FastAPI, React, SQLAlchemy, SQLite, and Tailwind CSS. The application provides secure authentication, product management, shopping cart functionality, search, filtering, pagination, and a responsive user interface.

---

## Features

### User Authentication

* User Registration
* User Login
* JWT Authentication
* Protected Routes
* Logout Functionality

### Product Management

* View Products
* Search Products
* Category Filtering
* Product Pagination
* Product Details
* Dynamic Product Images

### Shopping Cart

* Add Products to Cart
* Update Product Quantity
* Remove Products from Cart
* Cart Total Calculation
* Dynamic Cart Updates

### User Interface

* Responsive Design
* Tailwind CSS Styling
* Navigation Bar
* Home Page Carousel
* Featured Collections
* About Us Page
* Support Page

---

## Technology Stack

### Frontend

* React.js
* React Router DOM
* Axios
* Tailwind CSS
* React Icons

### Backend

* FastAPI
* SQLAlchemy
* Pydantic
* JWT Authentication
* SQLite Database

---

## Project Structure

Frontend

```text
src/
├── components/
├── pages/
├── layouts/
├── context/
├── Apis/
└── assets/
```

Backend

```text
app/
├── auth/
├── routers/
├── models/
├── database/
└── main.py
```

---

## API Endpoints

### Authentication

```http
POST /auth/register
POST /auth/token
GET /auth/me
```

### Products

```http
GET /products/
GET /products/{id}
POST /products/
PUT /products/{id}
DELETE /products/{id}
```

### Cart

```http
POST /cart/add
GET /cart/
PUT /cart/{item_id}
DELETE /cart/{item_id}
```

